title: Real Humans S1 Ep4
description:
Real Humans S1 Ep4

Semi-Human Rights - In a parallel present day, robots have become so human it is barely possible to distinguish them from real people. In this episode, Therese and Pilar feel humiliated when their hubot boyfriends aren't treated as humans. At the same time, Roger's anti-hubot group begins plotting violence. But why is Bea acting so strangely? And how does she know Niska? Stars Andreas Wilson, Lisette Pagler and Pia Halvorsen. 

From Sweden, in Swedish 

Subtitles by SBS AU TV
